<item>
            <title>[WICKET-1721] FormTester doesnt support onSelectionChanged  for RadioChoice</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-1721</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is not possible to test onSelectionChanged for RadioChoice and probably also other form components.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See this thread:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/Problem-test-RadioChoice-td18196023.html#a18196023&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/Problem-test-RadioChoice-td18196023.html#a18196023&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Doesn&amp;#39;t matter</environment>
